Job description 1 : 

- Candidate must have minimum 1+ year rich experience in new client acquisition, procurement and business development activities.
- Strong knowledge in pre-sales and post-sales activities.
- Should be good in lead generation and getting the key contact details of clients.
- Must have the ability to generate potential leads and to identify potential customers.
- Ability to make 100 calls per day.
- Responsible for the entire tie up process from the beginning to end.
- Skills: Lead Generation, Prospect Research, Contact Identification, Sales Outreach and Follow-Ups, Objection Handling, Business Development, Opportunity Identification.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job description 2 : 

What you will do:
Continuous research and understanding of prospective and current clients' business and industry. You will perform competitor benchmarking in terms of practices, processes, and policies.
You are expected to understand business processes, evaluate them, and identify areas of improvements.
Create data automations and validations using Excel and Google Sheets.

Associated Skills:
Market Research, Industry Scanning, Competitor Review, Data Analysis, KPI Definition and Tracking, MS Office Suite, Spreadsheet-Based Analysis, Client Advisory, Root Cause Identification.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

