- Strong understanding of change management principles to facilitate successful implementation of initiatives.
- Experience in stakeholder engagement to effectively gather requirements and align project objectives.

Skills:
Business Transformation Support, Process Improvement Assistance, Change Enablement Support, Project Management, Task Tracking, Timeline Awareness, Stakeholder Management, Expectation Alignment.

